data.description: This home is located in a desirable Hurst subdivision and Birdville ISD.  This single-story home has a great floorplan, with a swing rear entry garage, and no alley. Beautiful leaded glass windows in the formal dining room, wood paneling in the oversized living area with a floor-to-ceiling brick fireplace.  So many great remodeling opportunities for this great home.  The roof and solar panels are about two years old and the best part is the solar panels are owned and will convey with the home.  This is a great money-saving opportunity for the buyers.  Within minutes of the Chisholm Aquatic Center, park, and pond.
